<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="inch-n">inch <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪntʃ/    美 /ɪntʃ/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-254">1.★ <strong>[长度单位，等于2.54厘米] 英寸：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I'm five feet six inches tall.
我身高5英尺6英寸。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="by-an-inch-inches">by an inch / inches</h3>
<p>1.<strong>差一点儿；险些：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The car missed my dog by inches. 
那辆汽车差一点儿撞到我的狗。</p></div>

<h3 id="inch-by-inch">inch by inch</h3>
<p>1.<strong>缓慢地；一点一点地：</strong>  </p></div>